## ğŸš€ The Idea: Agentic Workforces

Software is shifting from tools you operate to teammates you assign work to.

I call this shift **agentic workforces**:
- not generic assistants,  
- not one-off scripts,  
- but scoped, reliable agents that own real responsibilities.

These agents:
- observe  
- reason  
- take action  
- report back  
- and stay inside clear boundaries

My work is about making that concept real inside actual products, not just demos.

